description: This source file, dslh_wmpdo_interface.c, contains utility functions related to the creation of a Wmp Database object within the DSL Home Model implementation. It includes licensing information, copyright notices, module description, and the implementation of the DslhCreateWmpDatabase function.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE DslhCreateWmpDatabase(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates and returns a handle to a new Wmp Database object, taking container, owner, and reserved contexts as parameters.
